casebody.data:
Ibis RODRIGUEZ and Antolin Rodriguez, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
U.S. BANK, N.A., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1951 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 14, 2017

ORDERED that appellants' motion for voluntary dismissal of appeal is recognized by the Court, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
